data.description: HUGE 3 BEDROOM,3 BATH HOME WITH MASTER ON THE MAIN.AWESOME MOUNTAIN VIEW AND WATERFALL SOUND FROM UPPER AND LOWER PORCHES.REDUCED OVER $80,000 FROM ORIGINAL LIST PRICE.VAULTED CEILING GREAT ROOM WITH BIG STONE FIREPLACE AND DOUBLE SLIDERS TO PORCH.LOWER LEVEL HAS ANOTHER BEDROOM AND BATH WITH MEDIA/GAME ROOM.4TH BEDROOM IS NOT FINISHED, CAN BE STUDIO, WORKSHOP OR BEDROOM.GREAT PRIVACY WITH THIS END OF ROAD PROPERTY.EASY ACCESS TO THE SKY VALLEY COUNTRY CLUB, GOLF COURSE, POOL AND TENNIS CLUB.IDEALLY LOCATED CLOSE TO BOTH HIGHLAND, NC AND DILLARD, GA.
